data.description: Inglewood Park has it all! Get incredible value in a convenient location just 2 miles to I-20 and minutes to the historic square in Covington. Open the door to a formal dining room that is perfect for entertaining family and friends. The spacious island kitchen opens to a casual breakfast area and flows effortlessly into a generous family room. Cabinet color options include gray, white and espresso. Upstairs offers a private bedroom suite with spa-like bath, plus large secondary bedrooms. And you will never be too far from home with Home Is Connected.® Your new home is built with an industry leading suite of smart home products that keep you connected with the people and place you value most. Photos used for illustrative purposes and do not depict actual home.
